TCBee release binaries include statically or dynamically linked third-party
software. The following copyright notices and license terms apply.

tcbee-record, tcbee-process: fully static binaries, no runtime system
  library dependencies.
tcbee-viz, tcbee-live: dynamically linked; require libGL/libEGL and
  Wayland or X11 libraries from the host system at runtime.

